<p>I want know how append method working in the following code. </p>  <pre><code>public class Main { public static void modifyBuffer(StringBuilder x) {     x.delete(0, x.length());     x.append("Edited"); }  public static void main(String[] args) {     StringBuilder Object = new StringBuilder("Original");     System.out.println("Object before modifying : " + Object);     modifyBuffer(Object);     System.out.println("Object after modifying : " + Object);  } } </code></pre>  <p>Output</p>  <pre><code>Object before modifying : Original Object after modifying : Edited </code></pre>